data.description: This Condron built 4-level is the best-priced home in the popular Bluegrass neighborhood! 4 bedrooms/3 baths. Lots of wonderful improvements here: xeriscape front yard installed in 2022, new roof with lifetime warranty in 2022, solar system installed in 2022 for reduced energy bills, new Trex decking in 2018, new security system, new front step railings and new garage door system all in 2023. Wonderful floor plan. LVP flooring in kitchen and dining area. All appliances stay including front-loading washer and dryer. Spacious primary bedroom. Main floor utilities. Gas stove in family room. Covered deck. Raised garden beds. Finished garage. Centrally located to all things northside.
